data.description: Welcome to this extraordinary 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo in the highly sought-after Trails End Villas community of Palm Beach Gardens. A true gem, this unit stands out as it comes complete with its own washer and dryer - a rare find in most units in the community! As you step inside, you'll be greeted by beautifully laid diagonal tile and upgraded crown molding throughout the main living area. The open concept kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring solid wood cabinetry with upgraded hardware, exquisite granite countertops complemented by a stone tile backsplash, and upgraded LED recessed lighting. The oversized living room is an inviting space with an upgraded fan, crown molding, and sliding glass doors leading to a private screened-in balcony - the perfect spot to unwind and enjoy the outdoors. The master bedroom offers comfort and style with diagonal tile floors, an upgraded fan, ample closet space, and large windows adorned with upgraded treatments. The master bathroom is equally impressive, featuring a solid wood vanity, upgraded light fixture, and a beautifully tiled walk-in shower with upgraded hardware. The secondary bedroom echoes the same level of quality, boasting diagonal tile floors, an upgraded fan, generous closet space, and well-lit windows with upgraded treatments. The corresponding bathroom includes a solid wood vanity, a framed mirror, an upgraded light fixture, and a shower/tub combo with upgraded hardware. The property boasts all impact windows and newer A/C (2020). Residents of Trails End Villas have access to a community clubhouse and pool, adding to the appeal of this wonderful living space. The monthly HOA covers essential amenities such as water, sewer, basic cable, trash, exterior maintenance, and exterior insurance. Convenience is at your doorstep with nearby Publix, Dunkin Donuts, CVS, Taco Chula, shops, the Gardens Green Market, Burns Road Community Center, PBG municipal sports complex, and parks. Additionally, the location offers easy access to the Gardens Mall, Whole Foods, Trader Joes, restaurants, shopping, I-95 & Turnpike, and is only 5 miles away from the beach. Don't miss the opportunity to make this meticulously maintained condo your new home.
